/**
*
*  Linux system programming
*  Process Subsystem
**/

Assignment : Write a program which is used to create deamon process.

Description :
This program creates the daemon process and it will write to the file which is supplied to it.
With ps -xj | grep <name of prog> we can check if our daemon process is working or not.

Note : No validations are applied. It is assumed that the user will enter only regular file.
